room_title: Escape room "Framed" by Out Of Time Escape in Charlotte
room_address: 16325 Northcross Drive, Suite B, Huntersville, NC 28078
room_description: One of your crazy friends has been accused of a crime in a small town in the boondocks. Can you break into the sheriff's office while the corrupt officers are on patrol? You have one hour to free your friend or face the same fate!
